# (#21) Search pattern highlighted when it isn't supposed to be
Given:
  test this
  test this

Execute (Search, move, and cancelled search):
  execute "normal /test\<cr>"
  Assert !empty(filter(getmatches(), "v:val.group == 'ObliqueCurrentMatch'")),
    \ 'Should highlight current match'
  normal! w
  doautocmd CursorMoved
  Assert empty(filter(getmatches(), "v:val.group == 'ObliqueCurrentMatch'")),
    \ 'Should clear highlight when cursor is moved'
  execute "normal /this\<bs>\<bs>\<bs>\<bs>"
  Assert empty(filter(getmatches(), "v:val.group == 'ObliqueCurrentMatch'")),
    \ 'Cancelled search should not restore highlight'

